	DETAILS OF THE NA AND NCOP SITTINGS ARE AS FOLLOWS:
	Date: Thursday, 17 October 2019
	Time: 14.00
	Venue: National Assembly Chamber, Parliament 
	
	Question and answer session to the Governance Cluster 3:
	Date: Thursday, 17 October 2019
	Time: 14.00
	Venue: National Council of Provinces Chamber, Parliament
	
	
	Journalists and photographers who do not have Parliamentary media access permits and wish to cover the sitting must send their details to Manelisi Ntsodo at mntsodo@parliament.gov.za  or 081 716 2021 / 021 403 8494.
